.TH "LIGHTNING-PAYMENT-LIST-FAILED" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-payment-list-failed \- list failed outbound payments, newest first
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning payment-list-failed
.RB [ --limit
.IR N ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns failed payments sorted by creation time descending.
Default limit is 50.
Returns an empty array if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{payment_hash, destination, amount_msat, created_at}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-payment-list (1),
.BR lightning-payment-status (1)
